1
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,120
Shuyi, you came to see me in such a hurry.

2
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,250
Is something wrong?

3
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,920
Lu Jingheng, I want to marry you.

4
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,979
Let's get married.

5
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,880
What?

6
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,680
Jingheng, please help me.

7
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:49,000
Just pretend.

8
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,320
If you propose,

9
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,180
my family will definitely agree.

10
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,920
Shuyi, calm down.

11
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,520
You want me to propose to you.

12
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,160
I can't do that.

13
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,780
Your room looks exactly the same.

14
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,130
It hasn't changed a bit.

15
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:07,960
I'm used to it.

16
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,660
Let's talk about business first.

17
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,920
Okay, business first.

18
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,880
Regarding this PR crisis,

19
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,640
I came up with a

20
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,320
bait-and-switch solution.

21
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,920
It will calm the public opinion

22
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:22,520
without damaging the Lu family's reputation.

23
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,170
You can't tell, can you?

24
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,160
We edited the photo

25
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,490
and replaced your wife with Tang Lili.

26
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,200
Tang Lili?

27
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,960
We spent the whole morning

28
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,480
comparing the figures

29
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,640
of the people around your wife.

30
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,920
Only Tang Lili's figure

31
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,450
is the most similar to hers.

32
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,520
The photo is already blurry.

33
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,600
We just need Tang Lili to come forward

34
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,530
and say she's the girl in the photo.

35
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,480
This way,

36
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:00,560
Shen Zhixia's scandal will be cleared.

37
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,620
This has nothing to do with Tang Lili.

38
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,580
It also concerns her reputation.

39
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:08,080
She shouldn't have to bear the public's judgment.

40
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,400
And even if she agrees,

41
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,760
Zhixia won't agree.

42
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,560
Shen Zhixia?

43
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,200
Maybe she will.

44
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,720
After all,

45
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:19,340
this is the fastest way to solve the problem.

46
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,780
I've already talked to Tang Lili.

47
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,320
But he didn't make things difficult for her,

48
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:31,050
and instead asked her to get your wife's opinion.

49
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,480
Miss Wen,

50
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,640
will this method

51
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:39,079
really help the Young Madam solve her troubles?

52
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,010
Of course it can.

53
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,800
It's just unfair to you.

54
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,360
The two of you need to discuss it carefully.

55
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,160
Young Madam.

56
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,280
Come in.

57
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,530
Young Madam.

58
00:03:59,120 --> 00:03:59,880
The eldest young master said

59
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:02,210
to bring up some pastries for you to taste.

60
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,400
Lili,

61
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:08,960
you came before I even finished peeling the egg.

62
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,960
Take it back to reduce the swelling.

63
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,690
Thank you, Young Madam.

64
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,200
Tell me when it's better.

65
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,160
Young Madam,

66
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,560
I still have clothes to wash,

67
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,680
so I'll take my leave.

68
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,480
Bye.

69
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,760
Let me guess what you're worried about.

70
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,280
Are you worried that Shen Zhixia will agree,

71
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,480
or that she won't?

72
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,440
She won't agree.

73
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,040
Let's change our plan.

74
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,930
Do you know your wife very well?

75
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,400
I heard rumors that

76
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,080
the Shen family used some extreme methods

77
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,810
to force you into the marriage.

78
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,560
Jingheng.

79
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:59,240
You don't have to hide anything from me.

80
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,300
No matter what others say,

81
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,690
Shen Zhixia will always be my wife.

82
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:06,340
I don't want her to bear the public's gossip.

83
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:11,880
Come in.

84
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,960
Young Master, Miss Wen.

85
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,730
What did Mrs. Lu say?

86
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,600
Young Madam... Young Madam agreed.

87
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,280
We decided this together.

88
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,760
She said she would compensate me afterwards,

89
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,240
and give me a lot of money.

90
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,360
And I was willing.

91
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,400
Jingheng.

92
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,400
Looks like I don't need to prepare another plan.

93
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,560
Your wife is very smart.

94
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,040
The media can come over anytime.

95
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,170
Get yourself ready.

96
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,480
Where's my phone?

97
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,680
Lili.

98
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,160
Who locked my door?

99
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,280
Are the equipment set up?

100
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:23,760
All set.

101
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,720
Please make a final check.

102
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,400
Okay.

103
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,440
Sorry for the trouble.

104
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,560
I'll definitely visit and thank you another day.

105
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,200
Okay.

106
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:35,170
It's no trouble. I'll definitely complete the task.

107
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:44,130
Waiting for your wife to come down.

108
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,840
Since you've decided to sacrifice others,

109
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:49,100
avoiding suspicion is understandable.

110
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:51,960
Jingheng,

111
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,220
why don't we make a bet?

112
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,200
Let's neither of us go call her,

113
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,130
and see if she comes down on her own.

114
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,920
Tang Lili,

115
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,450
if you don't want to,

116
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,080
the press conference can be stopped now.

117
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,340
Don't force yourself.

118
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,320
I...

119
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:13,760
Brother, this isn't right.

120
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,120
You asked her if she wanted to.

121
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,960
Why didn't you ask me?

122
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,280
Making me have a scandal with a servant

123
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,680
makes me lose face.

124
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,360
I did this entirely for you

125
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,160
and the Lu family's reputation.

126
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,600
How will you compensate me?

127
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,330
This has nothing to do with you.

128
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,160
Get out.

129
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,640
Be polite.

130
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:38,000
What? You want to hit me again?

131
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,170
There are reporters everywhere outside.

132
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,800
I dare you to touch me.

133
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,159
Watch me.

134
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,800
You...

135
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,280
So what if there are reporters?

136
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,880
Do I need to pick a day to hit you?

137
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:52,120
Our Lili earns money with her own hands.

138
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,120
You are just a loser.

139
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,480
How dare you be picky?

140
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,000
Let me tell you.

141
00:07:56,560 --> 00:08:00,000
I will explain my own matters to the reporters myself.

142
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,960
I will make it clear to everyone today.

143
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,440
Miss Shen. Miss Shen.

144
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,440
You all want to know

145
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,480
the story behind this scandalous photo.

146
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,280
Before I got married,

147
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,880
Lu Jingxi and I indeed had an immature relationship.

148
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,560
Miss Shen.

149
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,960
You dated Lu Jingxi before your marriage,

150
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:21,920
but now you are married to his brother.

151
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,120
Is there any fraud involved?

152
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,840
What do you take these two brothers for?

153
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,320
You knew you had a dark past,

154
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,680
yet you still married into the Lu family.

155
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,800
Are you intentionally bringing a stain

156
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,840
to drag down the Lu family's reputation?

157
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,280
Don't you feel guilty at all?

158
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:33,600
My relationship with Lu Jingxi was indeed before my marriage.

159
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,480
At that time, I had no interaction with Lu Jingheng.

160
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,640
How can it be called a fraud?

161
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,400
What?

162
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,679
Having a past relationship before marriage

163
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,840
means you don't deserve a marriage?

164
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,960
What kind of twisted logic is that?

165
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,520
Furthermore,

166
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,080
the term 'dark past',

167
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,080
don't you find it ridiculous to say?

168
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,080
When they were young,

169
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,680
who hasn't dated a few times?

170
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,680
Relentlessly clinging to others' privacy

171
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,000
and digging it up to grab attention,

172
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,160
you think you are so special, huh?

173
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,640
Trying to emotionally blackmail me?

174
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,960
I won't buy it.

175
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,640
But I heard you forced a Lu family maid

176
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,600
to be your scapegoat.

177
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,930
How do you explain this?

178
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,440
Me standing here taking your slander

179
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,500
is my explanation.

180
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,600
As for you,

181
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,800
care to explain to me

182
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,880
where you heard this

183
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,080
and if you have proof?

184
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,200
Making false claims without evidence.

185
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,400
Do you even deserve to be a reporter?

186
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,120
Even if that's not true,

187
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,160
you just admitted

188
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,600
your past with the second young master of the Lu family.

189
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,760
Don't you care at all about

190
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,760
the Lu family's reputation?

191
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,480
What happened between Lu Jingheng and me is our business.

192
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,000
It's not for others to judge.

193
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,680
As for the Lu family's reputation,

194
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,840
standing here and making things clear

195
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,960
is already considering the Lu family's reputation.

196
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,160
Instead of letting rumors

197
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,880
actually hurt my family,

198
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,360
I'd rather put an end

199
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,800
to these false speculations.

200
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,320
Get out of the way.

201
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,160
Miss Shen. Miss Shen. Miss Shen.

202
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:39,000
Miss Shen. Miss Shen.

203
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,520
Aunt.

204
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,240
Did you see the press conference today?

205
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,960
As for that woman Shen Zhixia,

206
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,680
in front of so many people,

207
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:59,400
she actually admitted her past with my cousin.

208
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,760
And she rebutted those reporters

209
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,560
so hard they couldn't say a word.

210
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,520
Lu Jingheng actually stood by her side,

211
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,160
even saying he could accept her past.

212
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,160
He can accept this kind of thing?

213
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:11,920
Right?

214
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,360
I really can't figure it out either.

215
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,770
She is involved in such a huge scandal,

216
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,240
yet Jingheng not only doesn't blame her,

217
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,970
but actually stands on her side

218
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,660
and defends her at every turn.

219
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,640
Aunt.

220
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,080
Aunt.

221
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,360
You must help me, Aunt.

222
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,680
We can't let Shen Zhixia

223
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,440
gain a firm foothold in the Lu family.

224
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:39,370
If Shen Zhixia secures her position in the Lu family,

225
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,760
then my chances of marrying Jingheng

226
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,620
will be even more hopeless, Aunt.

227
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:46,450
It's because the person you found is useless.

228
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,640
A reporter

229
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,640
who can't even say a complete sentence,

230
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,900
and let Shen Zhixia steal the spotlight.

231
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,160
I gave you the idea.

232
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,800
You're just useless.

233
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,240
Enough. Get out.

234
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,960
Leave me alone.

235
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,840
I understand, Aunt.

236
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,800
Shuyi.

237
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,680
Come here.

238
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,000
Sorry,

239
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,360
I was late picking her up.

240
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,560
Let me introduce you.

241
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,120
This is my cousin Shuyi.

242
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,760
And this is my girlfriend Yixin.

243
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,600
Hello, Miss Wen. Nice to meet you.

244
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,400
Nice to meet you too.

245
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,460
Please have a seat.

246
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:45,850
Would you like a drink, Miss Yixin?

247
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,040
I'm sorry.

248
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,440
I didn't mean it.

249
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,400
Here.

250
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,440
Go to the restroom and clean up.

251
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,900
I'll have my assistant bring you a new dress.

252
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,440
You are in a bad mood.

253
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,560
Why pick on her?

254
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:15,000
Haven't seen you for so many years.

255
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,660
Your taste is so bad, brother.

256
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,980
What kind of girl I choose,

257
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,800
as long as I like her, that's fine.

258
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:23,600
Tell me.

259
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:25,000
Why did you ask me out?

260
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,280
Do family members need a reason to meet?

261
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,200
Okay, I'll give it to you.

262
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,400
I came back this time

263
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,560
to test Lu Jingheng.

264
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,010
You are friends.

265
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,000
Help me.

266
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,560
Stop messing around.

267
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,980
Jingheng is already married.

268
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,690
But that's just how I am.

269
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,440
The more untouchable something is,

270
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:52,180
the more I want to get closer to it.

271
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,880
I will not help you.

272
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,280
I'm warning you.

273
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:09,960
Don't mess around.

274
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,080
You guys.

275
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,680
I argued all afternoon,

276
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:27,040
and my throat is still dry.

277
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,000
Have some water, Young Madam.

278
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,200
Drink some water.

279
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,320
Young Madam.

280
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,400
You really did us proud today.

281
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,600
I was worried before

282
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,120
that you'd let Lili be wronged.

283
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,040
But not only did you not do that,

284
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:40,640
you even fought the Second Young Master for her.

285
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:43,160
The Second Young Master always gives us a hard time.

286
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:45,090
Only you dare to teach him a lesson.

287
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,880
All right.

288
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,440
We are all just here to work.

289
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:52,360
We are equals.

290
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:54,520
The Young Madam treats us so well, right?

291
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,850
Thank you, Young Madam.

292
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:57,960
Stop.

293
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,120
Lili,

294
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:00,880
come with me.

295
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:02,680
Okay.

296
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,800
You,

297
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,760
don't do silly things like this again.

298
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:12,420
There's no reason to wrong yourself for others.

299
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:15,600
I'm mainly afraid that you'll be entangled in scandal

300
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,920
and the Lu family will make things difficult for you.

301
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:20,240
I will solve my own problems.

302
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:24,120
You must put yourself first in the future.

303
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:24,800
Understood?

304
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:26,360
Understood, Young Madam.

305
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,320
Come in.

306
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,480
Eldest Young Master.

307
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:36,120
Young Madam, I'll take my leave now.

308
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,480
You admitted your past with Lu Jingxi

309
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:47,080
in front of reporters.

310
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,570
Aren't you afraid public opinion will get worse?

